CURSED PRINCESS CLUB starring Kimiko Glenn

@KimikoGlenn becomes the beloved Princess Gwendolyn in this short film. Gwen isn’t like the rest of her sisters, but she still deserves a happily ever after.
 
#CursedPrincessClub #WEBTOON #WEBTOONobsessed
